1211
01:00:56,160 --> 01:00:58,240
Listen, I am Somya Chawla Dubey.

1212
01:00:58,560 --> 01:01:00,040
Chawla Dubey?

1213
01:01:00,120 --> 01:01:00,960
Yes.

1214
01:01:01,040 --> 01:01:02,880
- Two last names, huh?
- Yes.

1215
01:01:04,200 --> 01:01:05,720
